The two-step workflow to generate image with consistent style featuring the same character

* Step 1: Copy and paste the first block of text into Gemini along with your artifacts (e.g. article). Gemini will analyze the themes and fill in the visual metaphors, returning a completed text prompt.
* Step 2: Review the completed prompt text. If you like the metaphor, copy and paste the second block of text, ensuring attached image (your avatar reference) is attached to the same message.

---

Step 1: The Ideation and Metaphor Prompt

[Copy and paste this text into Gemini first, followed by your draft article.]

